# This directory holds live capture data synced from Ubuntu Server.
# Files here are excluded by .gitignore — never committed.
#
# To populate this directory, run from project root:
#
#   scp terickson@100.82.166.75:/opt/cowrie-logs/cowrie_enriched.json data\live\cowrie_enriched.json
#   scp terickson@100.82.166.75:/opt/cowrie-logs/nginx/access.log data\live\nginx_access.log
#
# See data/README.md for full instructions.
